nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 193 is the 171st issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the 101st issue published by Titan Magazines. It was published on October 30, 2019.

Our ongoing journey through the Skywalker Saga reaches its penultimate chapter! Plus: visit Ahch-To, as we make the trip to the real-life filming locations in Ireland. Discover the Secret Life of Porgs, as we find out more about their biology and how they were created for the movie. Learn the history behind some of the galaxy's more exotic names, and how you can create your own. And separate the truths from the white lies of the Star Wars universe in a special fact-or-fiction file!
